  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in order for you to go to see your Aunt Zelda, for the other side, you either had to go to some point of that street or some distance to get into a gate to either cross it or to a, a shorter way where they would make-- where they built bridges, where you virtually had to cross over a bridge to go on the other side.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the order was that children-- which I was one of those-- qualified, we had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked in a furniture-- wood finishing place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was, at that time, seven, seven years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were required to have identification cards to-- that we had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked in this Tischler Resort.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A Tischler Resort is where you build-- make furniture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my job was to just polish, all day long, the wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would give us this chemical, and we'd just put this chemical on, on, on unfinished wood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was-- methodically, we were just being shrunk into a-- into a-- in a sort of a cubicle, where our freedoms, our lives, our existence, our anything, was being denied us on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So again, I go back to the point that the wonderful thing, still, about the ghetto-- you know this thing has so many tentacles-- that it was wonderful at that particular time because of this, and the next time it was-- got worse, but it was still good because of that.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the third time that was taken away from you, it was still wonderful, because you were still able to play and do this a little bit or that.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
